Eric Fishwick, head of economic 
research at CLSA Asia-Pacific Markets in  Hong Kong , talks about 
Europe's sovereign debt crisis.  Fishwick also discusses People's Bank of China monetary 
policy and the outlook for Asian economies. He speaks with John 
Dawson on Bloomberg Television's "Asia Edge."  (Source: 
